text: Frederick "Fred" Unwin (5 October 1889 - 28 May 1965) was a British swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1890 births Category:1965 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Maldon District
